<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Dokumentasi BigLedger – Tutorial</title><link>https://www.bigledger.com/ms/tutorials/</link><description>Recent content in Tutorial on Dokumentasi BigLedger</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>ms</language><atom:link href="https://www.bigledger.com/ms/tutorials/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Mencipta Invois Pertama Anda</title><link>https://www.bigledger.com/ms/tutorials/first-invoice/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.bigledger.com/ms/tutorials/first-invoice/</guid><description>
&lt;p&gt;Panduan langkah demi langkah untuk mencipta dan menghantar e-invois pertama anda.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Prasyarat&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="prasyarat"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#prasyarat" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pelanggan dicipta dalam sistem&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Produk/perkhidmatan dikonfigurasikan&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tetapan cukai selesai&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Modul e-invois diaktifkan&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Langkah&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="langkah"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#langkah" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;1. Cipta Pesanan Jualan&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="1-cipta-pesanan-jualan"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#1-cipta-pesanan-jualan" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Navigasi ke &lt;strong&gt;Sales&lt;/strong&gt; → &lt;strong&gt;Internal Sales Order&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;2. Tambah Pelanggan&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="2-tambah-pelanggan"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#2-tambah-pelanggan" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Pilih atau cipta pelanggan&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;3. Tambah Item&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="3-tambah-item"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#3-tambah-item" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tambah produk/perkhidmatan dengan kuantiti&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;4. Semak Harga&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="4-semak-harga"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#4-semak-harga" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Semak harga, diskaun, cukai&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;5. Jana Invois&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="5-jana-invois"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#5-jana-invois" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Klik &lt;strong&gt;Create Invoice&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;6. Hantar ke LHDN&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="6-hantar-ke-lhdn"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#6-hantar-ke-lhdn" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Invois dihantar secara automatik&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;7. Jejak Status&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="7-jejak-status"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#7-jejak-status" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Pantau status penghantaran&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Tutorial Video&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="tutorial-video"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#tutorial-video" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="#" &gt;Tonton panduan video&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Perlukan bantuan? Hubungi &lt;a href="mailto:support@bigledger.com" &gt;support@bigledger.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Proses Penutupan Akhir Bulan</title><link>https://www.bigledger.com/ms/tutorials/month-end-closing/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.bigledger.com/ms/tutorials/month-end-closing/</guid><description>
&lt;p&gt;Lengkapkan prosedur akhir bulan dalam BigLedger.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Senarai Semak&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="senarai-semak"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
